Package KI305.Panasiuk.Lab7

Class TrashCan<T extends Item>

java.lang.Object
KI305.Panasiuk.Lab7.TrashCan<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of items that the trash can can hold, must implement the Item interface.
public class TrashCan<T extends Item> extends Object
A generic class representing a trash can that can hold items of type T. It provides methods for adding, removing, checking emptiness, getting size, showing contents, clearing, and peeking into the trash can.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Taras Panasiuk
